properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 18 at 4:02AM EST until January 18 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Seas 5 to 8 feet.

* WHERE...Northeast Florida coastal waters from Fernandina Beach
FL to Flagler Beach FL out to 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 4 PM EST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON
